Project\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolygon","type":"reference"},{"text":" object, while the surrounding","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"atoll would be another. You could also use a multipolygon shape to represent a","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"group of disconnected but related buildings.","type":"text"}],"fragments":[{"text":"MLNMultiPolygon","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolygon","role":"symbol","type":"topic","title":"MLNMultiPolygon"}}}